docs.text: Overview ¶ Please note that the team name should be unique. Teams are a collection of servers which share properties, chats and much more. All invites will be deleted after 1 day to prevent spaming. Additionally you can only have 3 owning teams per server.
docs.title: Overview

docs.text: Please note that the team name should be unique. Teams are a collection of servers which share properties, chats and much more. All invites will be deleted after 1 day to prevent spaming. Additionally you can only have 3 owning teams per server.
docs.title: Overview

docs.text: Commands ¶ Command Permission Aliases Description create \ Manage server add, a, make, m + Create a team with that name. list Manage server ls, * List all teams the server are in delete \ Manage server rm, r, d, - Delete a team where you are owner leave \ Manage server l, # Leave a team invite \ Manage server i Invite a server to a team accept \ Manage server a Accept an invite decline \ Manage server d Decline an invite has \ Manage server h Test if you have an invite from this server
docs.title: Commands
